Sentence: Proximate composition, fatty acid profile, cholesterol, alpha - tocoferol content and essential ( K, Na, Cl, S, Mg, Ca, Zn, Cu, Fe, Mn, and Se) and contaminant element ( Hg / MeHg, Cd, Pb, and As) levels in silver scabbardfish ( Lepidopus caudatus), hake ( Merluccius merluccius), and ray ( Raja spp.) were investigated.
